					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>SCP-1727 is a ███ ███████ brand portable car wash, <strong>manufactured in 1999</strong>.</p> </blockquote> <blockquote> <p>A cover story regarding local pranksters was disseminated, with SCP-1727 being classified as Safe <strong>on 11/17/1987</strong>.</p> </blockquote> <p>The Foundation somehow managed to classify it as safe twelve years before it was created.</p> <p>&#8230;just sayin'.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
